00:21:58.716 --> 00:22:01.316 A:middle
to More Info and the
hint to Double-Tap

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:21:58.716 --> 00:22:01.316 A:middle
to More Info and the
hint to Double-Tap

00:22:01.346 --> 00:22:02.276 A:middle
To View More Information.

00:22:03.366 --> 00:22:04.916 A:middle
And obviously you would
want to localize this,

00:22:05.466 --> 00:22:08.496 A:middle
but for now we will
leave it this way.

00:22:09.706 --> 00:22:15.846 A:middle
The only other thing we want to
do here is set the Header trait

00:22:16.266 --> 00:22:19.256 A:middle
on the location and felt
header, so it's clear what's

00:22:19.356 --> 00:22:22.416 A:middle
in that view and
what information is

00:22:22.416 --> 00:22:23.106 A:middle
being communicated.

00:22:24.086 --> 00:22:28.076 A:middle
That was just a few minutes
of work, and that should clean

00:22:28.076 --> 00:22:29.146 A:middle
up quite a few issues.

00:22:29.306 --> 00:22:33.866 A:middle
Let's build and check it out.

00:22:33.866 --> 00:22:34.196 A:middle
All right.

00:22:34.196 --> 00:22:36.446 A:middle
Let's triple-tap home to
turn VoiceOver back on.

00:22:37.606 --> 00:22:38.226 A:middle
&gt;&gt; VOICEOVER: VoiceOver on.

00:22:38.456 --> 00:22:41.966 A:middle
FaceTime, QuakeWatch,
double-tap to open,

00:22:42.576 --> 00:22:44.456 A:middle
QuakeWatch, earthquakes,
heading.

00:22:46.366 --> 00:22:47.746 A:middle
&gt;&gt; IAN FISCH: The first
thing you notice is

00:22:47.746 --> 00:22:49.836 A:middle
that ugly yellow
color is finally gone.

00:22:50.216 --> 00:22:50.826 A:middle
Thank goodness!

00:22:51.656 --> 00:22:55.036 A:middle
So let's swipe around with one
finger and see what happens.

00:22:55.286 --> 00:22:57.666 A:middle
&gt;&gt; VOICEOVER: Favorites,
button, 12 kilometers,

00:22:57.936 --> 00:23:02.436 A:middle
Oklahoma, 2015, 10:57 a.m.

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:22:57.936 --> 00:23:02.436 A:middle
Oklahoma, 2015, 10:57 a.m.

00:23:02.436 --> 00:23:04.236 A:middle
&gt;&gt; IAN FISCH: So earthquake
finds the cell now.

00:23:04.546 --> 00:23:10.716 A:middle
That's good if we come
to the detail view.

00:23:11.616 --> 00:23:14.566 A:middle
&gt;&gt; VOICEOVER: Dismiss
earthquake, location, heading.

00:23:14.966 --> 00:23:16.996 A:middle
&gt;&gt; IAN FISCH: Location
now has the heading trait,

00:23:17.086 --> 00:23:18.506 A:middle
so it's clear what's
happening in the view.

00:23:18.506 --> 00:23:19.096 A:middle
&gt;&gt; VOICEOVER: 12 kilometers.

