&gt;&gt; IAN FISCH: As I
slide my finger across,

00:30:16.276 --> 00:30:19.856 A:middle
I should hit all of them.

00:30:20.066 --> 00:30:23.486 A:middle
And that's how you make
a graphic accessible,

00:30:23.486 --> 00:30:24.976 A:middle
an earthquake graph
accessible, at least.

00:30:25.786 --> 00:30:27.836 A:middle
So just a few lines of
code, and we were able

00:30:27.836 --> 00:30:32.306 A:middle
to clean all of that up.

00:30:32.696 --> 00:30:33.786 A:middle
Let's take one more look,

00:30:33.786 --> 00:30:35.996 A:middle
we have the earthquake
cell is now accessible,

00:30:35.996 --> 00:30:37.596 A:middle
not using yellow
anymore, thank goodness.

00:30:38.186 --> 00:30:40.156 A:middle
The map detail is accessible.

00:30:40.526 --> 00:30:43.186 A:middle
We can add a favorite
using the Magic Tap,

00:30:44.146 --> 00:30:47.256 A:middle
and we can even explore the
graph and compare earthquakes,

00:30:47.746 --> 00:30:49.256 A:middle
our favorite earthquakes,
at least.

00:30:50.586 --> 00:30:52.826 A:middle
So just a few lines of
code, just a few minutes,

00:30:52.826 --> 00:30:55.816 A:middle
and we were able to take an app
that was completely unusable

00:30:55.816 --> 00:30:59.526 A:middle
for VoiceOver users and make
it probably the most accessible

00:30:59.526 --> 00:31:01.496 A:middle
earthquake tracking
app out there.

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:30:59.526 --> 00:31:01.496 A:middle
earthquake tracking
app out there.

00:31:04.926 --> 00:31:08.156 A:middle
Remember that accessibility
is about users.

00:31:08.346 --> 00:31:09.896 A:middle
Thinking about how users

00:31:09.896 --> 00:31:11.926 A:middle
of all abilities will
interact with your app.

00:31:12.596 --> 00:31:14.776 A:middle
Remember everyone that's
going to be using your app

00:31:14.776 --> 00:31:16.686 A:middle
as you are designing it.

00:31:16.836 --> 00:31:18.666 A:middle
Apple has been embracing
accessibility

00:31:18.666 --> 00:31:20.886 A:middle
for so long that's
it's expected of us

00:31:20.926 --> 00:31:24.176 A:middle
that we are fully accessible
with all of the products

00:31:24.176 --> 00:31:25.116 A:middle
and features that we release.

00:31:25.396 --> 00:31:30.586 A:middle
And we really strive hard
to make that possible.

